        <body>
            <pb n="1R"/>
            <p rend="align(right)"><placeName>Baltimore</placeName>, <date>Mai 13th 1867</date></p>
            <p>Dear Sir:</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">my friend <persName>Mr. N. Gotthelf</persName> of
                    <placeName>Washington</placeName>—<lb/>recommended me to you.</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)"><del>I am</del> I come from <placeName>Seligenstadt</placeName>
                <add>?</add><lb/>
                <add>?</add>. My son who works here as a<lb/> bookkeeper, as well as his boss, a
                    <persName>Mr. Selidenberg</persName><lb/> asked me to come here to act as a
                cantor and<lb/> teacher for the P<add>?</add> school. I came <del>to</del> with
                my<lb/> wife and three children but came <sic>to</sic> late and the job<lb/> had
                been given to someone else although the president<lb/> of the congregation knew
                about it; that is my start<lb/> in <placeName>America</placeName>. “All beginnings
                are hard” <add>כל ההתחלות קשות</add></p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">I know my job and was even a<lb/> preacher and was greatly
                acknowledged. I now<lb/> ask you to help me find <del>if</del> a <del>n
                    honorable</del><lb/> dignified job, if that is possible for you. A<lb/> job
                which is worthy of a gentleman, skilled in<lb/> learning <add>למדנות</add> liberal
                    <del>free</del> religion, according to the laws of <persName>Moses</persName>
                and of <placeName>Israel</placeName>—<add>כדת משה וישראל</add><lb/> I can bring
                excellent character and <add>?</add> references<lb/> as well as written testimonials
                showing that<lb/> I <del>am 30</del> have been in the service of Un.<lb/> .... for
                30 years. “A wise man will understand”<lb/>
                <add>ודי למבין</add></p>
            <pb n="2R"/>
            <p rend="align(right)">2</p>
            <p>I am looking forward to your reply and<lb/> am yours very truly</p>
            <p>(<persName role="author">Samuel</persName>) <hi rend="indent(4)"><persName
                        role="author">S. Kuttnauer</persName></hi></p>
            <p rend="indent(6)">
                <placeName>S. Bond St. 200</placeName>
            </p>
